<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Frequently Asked Questions</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 50px 0;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 2.5em;
        }

        .faq-section {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .faq-item {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .faq-item button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            outline: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .faq-item button:hover {
            background-color: #2980b9;
        }

        .faq-item button:focus {
            background-color: #2980b9;
        }

        .faq-answer {
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
            display: none;
            margin-top: 5px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #555;
            border-radius: 0 0 4px 4px;
        }

        .faq-answer p {
            margin: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h1>

        <div class="faq-section">
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="accordion">What is the return policy?</button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>You can return any items within 30 days of receiving your order, as long as the items are in their original condition with tags attached. Please refer to our Return & Exchange page for more details.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="accordion">How do I track my order?</button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Once your order has shipped, you will receive a tracking number via email. You can use this number to track your order through our courier's website.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="accordion">What payment methods do you accept?</button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>We accept a wide variety of payment methods, including credit cards (Visa, MasterCard, American Express), PayPal, and Apple Pay. You can choose your preferred method at checkout.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="accordion">How can I contact customer support?</button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>You can contact our customer support team via email at <a href="mailto:support@example.com">support@example.com</a> or by phone at +1 800 123 4567. We are available 24/7 to assist you.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="accordion">Do you offer international shipping?</button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Yes! We offer international shipping to most countries. Shipping rates vary depending on the destination. Please check our Shipping Information page for more details.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Get all the buttons with the "accordion" class
        var acc = document.getElementsByClassName("accordion");

        // Loop through all the buttons and add an event listener
        for (var i = 0; i < acc.length; i++) {
            acc[i].addEventListener("click", function () {
                // Toggle the 'active' class on the clicked button
                this.classList.toggle("active");

                // Get the corresponding answer
                var answer = this.nextElementSibling;

                // Toggle visibility of the answer
                if (answer.style.display === "block") {
                    answer.style.display = "none";
                } else {
                    answer.style.display = "block";
                }
            });
        }
    </script>

</body>

</html>
